data.description: Ready for a new family, established neighborhood close to Skyline Elementary School and Stillwater Junior High School. This home has 3 bedrooms ,2 bathrooms and 2 car garage. Covered patio in the back, large fenced yard, storage shed in the back for your garden implements. Refrigerator, washer and dryer remain with the property ,but are not warranted. Foundation was repaired 04/2023.
